and opinions, but also what that trailer meant

00:00:33.910 --> 00:00:37.810
to me, as a modder.

00:00:37.810 --> 00:00:46.350
I’ll preface myself saying that I’m doing
mods for the Arkhamverse since 2012, so,

00:00:47.480 --> 00:00:55.100
