and I would be blind if I didn’t noticed

00:01:12.000 --> 00:01:20.380
it. But what I’m saying is that the graphic
of the game wasn’t making me any surprise, y'know?

00:01:20.380 --> 00:01:31.720
Once the game was so delayed, like, months, and it’s been released to this new generation of consoles and PCs, I was indeed

00:01:31.720 --> 00:01:40.369
