really impressed with the graphics. I really wasn't, until

00:01:49.770 --> 00:01:54.990
trailer came out.    So, to be honest...

00:01:55.000 --> 00:02:02.360
I don’t exactly know WHAT was the thing
that make me so damn much impressed, in the trailer, but in

00:02:02.360 --> 00:02:08.939
