00:03:30.690 --> 00:03:38.349
haven’t noticed it before, but this game
is so fricking beautiful, man... I mean, those textures

00:03:38.349 --> 00:03:44.510
probably have four thousand pixels, dude. That's the double of the biggest one in Arkham Origins,

00:03:44.510 --> 00:03:53.550
